---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection';

const faqSchemaObject = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Do you offer commercial HVAC maintenance plans?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes — we offer custom maintenance plans for businesses including restaurants, offices, and retail spaces in Orange County."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How quickly can you respond to commercial HVAC emergencies?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "We prioritize commercial emergency calls and typically dispatch within 2 hours for businesses in Orange County."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What commercial HVAC systems do you work on?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "We service rooftop units, split systems, VRF/VRV systems, chillers, and packaged units for commercial properties."
      }
    }
  ]
};
---

<BaseLayout title="Commercial HVAC Services in Stanton, CA | HiLo Heating & Air" description="Professional commercial HVAC services for businesses in Stanton, CA. Installation, maintenance, emergency repairs, and replacements for offices, restaurants, and more." faqSchema={faqSchemaObject}>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-blue-800 py-20 sm:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Commercial HVAC Services in Stanton, CA</h1>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">A broken AC at home is annoying. A broken AC in a packed restaurant kitchen, mid-lunch rush? That's lost money, fast. Hilo Heating and Air handles commercial HVAC services for businesses around Stanton.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mt-0 mb-4">What Commercial HVAC Services Actually Involve</h2>

        <p>A broken AC at home is annoying. A broken AC in a packed restaurant kitchen, mid-lunch rush? That's lost money, fast. Hilo Heating and Air has handled <strong>commercial HVAC services</strong> for businesses around Stanton for years now, and we get it — downtime isn't just inconvenient for a business. It costs real money, every hour it drags on.</p>

        <h2>Commercial Isn't Just "Residential, But Bigger"</h2>
        <p>A lot of people assume that. It's not true. Different equipment entirely — rooftop units, multi-zone setups, sometimes separate systems running different parts of one building. Our <strong>commercial HVAC services</strong> cover offices, retail spaces, restaurants, warehouses, medical facilities. Each one's got its own quirks.</p>
        <p>A restaurant kitchen needs ventilation a retail store never will. A server room needs tighter temperature control than an open office floor. We've worked enough property types to know these aren't interchangeable jobs, and we treat them that way instead of running everyone through the same checklist.</p>

        <h2>What We Actually Do</h2>
        <p>Our <strong>commercial HVAC services</strong> span installation, ongoing maintenance contracts, emergency repairs, full replacements when a unit's finally done. We also handle ductwork — a lot of commercial cooling complaints actually trace back to leaky ducts, not the unit itself, and people miss that constantly.</p>
        <p>For businesses that can't eat unplanned downtime, we build maintenance schedules around your actual hours. Service before you open or after you close, not during your busiest two hours of the week. Rooftop units tend to fail quietly until they don't — which is exactly why regular checkups matter more here than people think.</p>

        <h2>Built Around Your Schedule, Not a Template</h2>
        <p>Every business is different. We try to actually work with that instead of running everyone through the same package. Restaurants get treated differently than offices. Retail's priorities aren't a warehouse's priorities. We talk through your specific setup — hours, system age, past problems — before recommending anything.</p>
        <p>When something breaks without warning, speed matters more here than in a house. An office with no AC in July isn't just uncomfortable. It's a productivity hit, and honestly, a liability concern too. We prioritize commercial emergencies with that in mind.</p>

        <h2>Why Stanton Businesses Call Hilo Heating and Air</h2>
        <p>Licensed, insured, and we've worked the harder jobs, not just the easy ones. We've built relationships here by showing up when we say we will and being straight about cost and timeline. A good chunk of our commercial clients started as a single emergency call — and just kept calling after that.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">What kinds of businesses do you work with?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Offices, restaurants, retail, warehouses, medical facilities — a wide mix.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Do you offer ongoing maintenance contracts?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, built around your hours and your specific equipment.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Can you install rooftop units?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Regularly, yes — it's a standard part of our commercial work.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How fast for an emergency call?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Usually same day. We know downtime hits your bottom line directly.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Can you work after hours?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, most maintenance and a lot of repairs can happen outside business hours.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Are techs trained on commercial systems specifically?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, not just residential equipment.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Do you handle full replacements?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, full evaluation through install and testing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Financing for commercial jobs?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, available for larger projects.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-brand-blue/5 py-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-brand-blue font-semibold">Hilo Heating and Air · 8131 Electric Ave, Stanton, CA 90680, United States</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-1"><a href="tel:+17148535534" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">(714) 853-5534</a> · <a href="mailto:info@hiloheatingandair.com" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">info@hiloheatingandair.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection client:visible />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
